::Aerotaur::
       He takes the shots from Carnatron in the chest, arms, and wings 
wincing with every hit.  It forces him back a step and he grimaces but spares 
a glance over his shoulder at Nightlight who he sees is unconscious.  
"Flicker, you can end this right now.  Tell him to cease fire and I'll take 
Nightlight home.  You've already got what you wanted, you're home free.  You 
don't need her anymore."

--part1_143.dc14e6c.2bba6700_boundary
